claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: Table presenting baseline demographic and clinical characteristics of study participants receiving RIV4 (Flublok) or SD-IIV4, including race, sex, season, age group, influenza case status, and high-risk condition, with P-values for differences between groups. does not support the claim because the table only shows participant demographics and clinical characteristics, with no information on antigenic match to WHO- or FDA-selected flu strains.
